Zimbabwean businessman Edward Chidziva has partnered with a reputable Dubai based businessman Umar Ali in a ground breaking deal that could solidify Zimbabwe and Dubai business relations. In a case of grass to grace, Chidziva who hails from Harare has broken barriers to find himself in the streets of Al bahja group in Dubai Chidziva joined the reputable company on the 22nd of December. The company has taken a new dimension and now exploring Africa for possible business opportunities. The company specializes in setting up businesses in Dubai, the services range from business consultancy, business visas, employment visas and facilitating relocations of organizations and individuals